---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GetQuoete from "../../../components/buttons/GetQuote.astro";
import Testimonials from "../../../components/Testimonials";
import ButtonScrollTop from "../../../components/buttons/ButtonScrollTop";
---
<link rel="canonical" href="https://cayadservices.com/for-individuals/open-car-transport" />
<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/open-trailer.webp") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>


<Layout title="Affordable Open Car Transport in the U.S | Cayad Auto Transport"
content="Looking for safe and affordable open car shipping in the U.S.? Cayad Auto Transport offers fast, reliable service with real-time quotes. Call now!">
  <div
    class="container-fluid flex flex-col items-center justify-center custom-background h-[60vh]"
  >
    <div class="w-[80%]">
      <p
        class="text-white text-[4rem] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-bold"
        data-aos="fade-down"
      >
      Open Auto Transport
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">
        Open auto transport is the most cost-effective way to ship your car in the U.S.
      </h1>
      <GetQuoete />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 flex justify-center mb-8">
    <Testimonials
      position="center"
      title="Verified Open Car Transport Testimonials"
      client:load
    />
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] text-[2.5rem]">
          What is <strong>open auto transport</strong>?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          <strong>Open auto transport</strong> is the most common and affordable option for <strong>car shipping</strong> in the U.S. It allows carriers to move up to 10 vehicles at once, making it faster to schedule and more budget-friendly than enclosed options. If you're looking for safe, reliable, and cost-effective shipping, this is it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/img/open-auto.webp" width="612" height="408" class="rounded-xl" alt="open car transport haul on the road"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full">
      <h2
        class="font-semibold xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:px-4 sm:px-4 xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] text-[2.5rem]"
      >
      Why Open Auto Transport Is the Smartest and Most Affordable Car Shipping Option:
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:px-4 sm:px-4">
      <div
        class="grid mt-8 grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 w-full gap-6"
      >
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.3s"
        >
        <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#00000] font-semibold">Fast and Reliable Shipping</h5>
        <p class="py-4">
          When time matters, <strong>open auto transport</strong> is your best bet. It’s the most widely used and efficient method, over 90% of carriers in the U.S. rely on <strong>open auto carriers</strong> for their speed, availability, and affordability. Want your car shipped quickly and without stress? Choose the trusted <strong>open car shipping</strong> solution.
        </p>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.5s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-black font-semibold">
              Affordable and Efficient
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4">
              Looking for the most budget-friendly solution? <strong>Open auto transport</strong> is the smartest choice. By transporting multiple vehicles at once, <strong>open carriers</strong> reduce operational costs, passing the savings directly to you.
            </p>            
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.7s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-black font-semibold">
              Top Load Open Auto Transport
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4 text-base text-black">
              <strong>Top load auto transport</strong> places your vehicle on the upper level of the trailer, protecting it from debris and leaks. It’s a smart upgrade in <strong>open car transport</strong> for added safety, without paying for enclosed shipping.
            </p>
                        
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.9s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl py-4 text-black font-semibold">
              Trusted by Car Dealerships
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4 text-base text-black">
              Top <a href="/for-businesses/auto-dealers/" class="text-btn-blue hover:underline">dealerships</a>  across the country rely on <strong>open auto transport</strong> to move inventory quickly and safely. At Cayad, we work with leading brands to deliver <strong>vehicle transport</strong> that’s fast, reliable, and cost-effective, even for brand-new cars.
            </p>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="w-full flex mb-8 flex-col items-center xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-0 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-0 mx-auto overflow-hidden px-0"
  >
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-4 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-4 py-10 px-0"
    >
    <h2 class="text-4xl text-[#00000] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-medium mb-10">
      Why Cayad is the Best Choice for Reliable Open Car Transport in the U.S.
    </h2>    
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 xs:grid-cols-1 gap-10"
      >
        <div class="wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/dollar.webp" width="1080" height="1080" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" alt="open car transport dollar logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-black">No Upfront Payment</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0 text-black">
                With <strong>Cayad Auto Transport</strong>, you only pay the deposit when your vehicle is dispatched to the carrier, no upfront fees.
              </p>


            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/countries.webp" width="1080" height="1080" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" alt="open car shipping counties logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-black">Best Price Guaranteed</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0 text-black">
                Our <strong>car shipping specialists</strong> analyze every factor to offer you the most accurate and fair <strong>open car transport cost</strong> no guesswork, just value.
              </p>

            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <img src="/img/easy.webp" width="1080" height="1080" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" alt="open auto transport easy logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-black">Friendly Car Shipping Support</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0 text-base text-black">
                Our team offers friendly, reliable assistance throughout your entire <strong>open car transport</strong> experience. From your first quote to final delivery, we’re here to guide you every step of the way.
              </p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-[95%] wow"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          style="min-height: 400px;"
        >
          <div class="h-full">
            <img
              src="/img/banner.webp"
              class="object-cover rounded-xl w-full h-full"
              width="1024" height="649"
              alt="open car shipping haul"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
</Layout>